#Text=Football : Ronaldo penalty sends United to FA Cup semifinals
#Text=Monday , March 19 , 2007
#Text=Manchester United 1 0 Middlesbrough F.C.
#Text=Match Stats

#Text=Attendance 71325 Goalscorers for Manchester United Ronaldo ( 76'(pen ) ) Goalscorers for Middlesbrough None Bookings ( Manchester United ) Smith , Rooney ( Yellow ( 2 ) ) Bookings ( Middlesbrough ) Xavier , Woodgate , Pogatetz , Boateng , Rochemback ( Yellow ( 5 ) ) , Morrison ( Red ( 1 ) )
#Text=A penalty by Cristiano Ronaldo in the 76th minute was all that separated Manchester United and Middlesbrough earlier today at Old Trafford .
#Text=The FA Cup 6th round replay was forced after a Ronaldo penalty a week ago which tied the last match at 2-2 , sending the second game to Old Trafford .
#Text=Middlesbrough started with the deadly strike pair of Mark Viduka and Yakubu up front , while Manchester had Alan Smith and Wayne Rooney as paired strikers .
#Text=United came out with the first good chances of the game as Wayne Rooney had an attempt on net , but saw his shot blocked by defender Jonathan Woodgate .
#Text=Nemanja Vidic then had a chance for United off a Giggs corner , but his powerful header was held by keeper Mark Schwarzer .
#Text=Ronaldo then had a shot on net after the ball fortuitously fell to his feet , but the Portuguese midfielders strike flew just wide .

#Text=Middlesbrough survived through the first onslaught and had their first real chance on 16 minutes when a deflected pass by Xavier found its way to Mark Viduka , but his shot flew wide of Tomasz Kuszczak 's goal .
#Text=Woodgate soon saved Middlesbrough again as he blocked a cross net pass from Ronaldo which was aimed for a wide open Alan Smith .
#Text=Wayne Rooney was then given a clear run in on goal after he was found by a well time through ball from Giggs , but Mark Schwarzer spread wide to snatch the ball from Rooney 's feet .
#Text=Mark Viduka then made space in the United penalty box and dropped off a pass for Stuart Downing , but his right footed shot flew wide yet again .
#Text=Ronaldo again threatened '
#Text=Boro , but he saw his wide angled shot bang off the post after rounding Schwarzer .
#Text=Rooney again was given a break away on net , but he was again stopped by the Australian Schwarzer .
#Text=Soon after , Jonathan Woodgate brought Ronaldo down in the box , and United were awarded a penalty .
#Text=Ronaldo sent the ball high and to the left of Schwarzer as the keeper went the wrong way , and United took the lead .
#Text=Middlesbrough had little more in the way of attacking threat , with a wide shot by Morrison being all they could muster .
#Text=The game did end on a sour note , however , after a few scuffles and a cynical challenge on Ronaldo by James Morrison saw several yellow cards handed out and Morrison was shown red .
#Text=United will take on Watford in the semifinals of the cup while Middlesbrough have only the Premier League to focus on now , with their next match being played at West Ham .
